name: iDuck
body:
### Welcome to iDuck! 
Duck is a simple web application, rebuilt for the mobile web. It is a learning exercise and has limited, if any, use for commercial implementation. 

### Authors and Contributors
Thanks to Chris Wanstrath (@defunkt), PJ Hyett (@pjhyett), and Tom Preston-Werner (@mojombo) who founded GitHub in 2007. If you have any questions about this project, please contact @3825 directly. We will read all messages but cannot guarantee a response. 

### Support or Contact
